<P><HI>THE</HI> Emperours Letters were seco<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> by others from the Councel to the Church<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> <HI>Alexandria, Lybia, Pentapolis,</HI> including joyfull newes of the <HI>Vnion</HI> of the Chri<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">
