<P><HI>MOREOVER</HI> the <HI>right hand</HI> is the high blessednesse, peace&punc; and joy, with satisfacti|on, which <HI>God</HI> hath in <HI>Christs</HI> holy society, upon the account of his obedience as Man in doing always his will, for the <HI>left</HI> in the Pa|rable, denots enmity, <HI>dissatisfaction</HI> and con|trariety,
